flowcoin (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Full node daemon with RandomX CPU-only Proof-of-Work consensus.
  * Ed25519 signatures; keccak256d for block IDs, merkle roots and
    address hashing.
  * SLIP-0010 HD key derivation.
  * Bech32 v0 address encoding (HRP: fl).
  * Bitcoin-compatible UTXO model, script system, and wire format.

